		"body": "# Description\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\n\r\nImproves the visual appearance of code blocks by adding padding, spacing, and rounded corners. There is no existing issue for this it’s a small visual enhancement. I’ve been using these styles locally via a custom stylesheet and found them useful, so thought maybe I submit a PR as well.\r\n\r\nApplies to:\r\n- Renderer\r\n- Editor\r\n\r\n## Screenshots\r\n\r\n### Before:\r\n<img width=\"1411\" height=\"605\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-04-22 193414\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3d86bbea-eaa6-4cee-b06e-d8cd69ad5a61\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n### After:\r\n<img width=\"1410\" height=\"625\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-04-22 222642\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/66a243bd-9bbe-4041-9f1c-4a47e78ef211\" />",
