			"updated_at": "2026-04-24T20:01:37Z",
			"body": "Such a change should be supported by a proper rationale. Whether it looks nicer or not is a matter of opinion and maybe a nicer look is not what we want, if it means it's less functional or achieve different goals than what the editor is meant for. So if you want to change something like this, you need to come with a better rationale than \"it improves the visual appearance\".\r\n\r\nSo for now I will close the PR. If you are interested in improving how the app looks, please discuss the changes first on the forum",
